1:1 Mbere na mbere hariho Jambo; Jambo uwo yahoranye n'Imana kandi Jambo yari Imana. 
1:2 Uwo yahoranye n'Imana mbere na mbere. 
1:3 Ibintu byose ni we wabiremye, ndetse mu byaremwe byose nta na kimwe kitaremwe na we. 
1:4 Muri we harimo ubugingo, kandi ubwo bugingo bwari Umucyo w'abantu. 
1:5 Uwo Mucyo uvira mu mwijima, ariko umwijima ntiwawumenya.</span><span class="note f"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body"><span class="fk">ntiwawumenya: </span><span class="ft"> cyangwa, ntiwawutsinda.
1:6   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Mat 3.1; Mar 1.4; Luka 3.1-2  
1:7 Uwo yazanywe no guhamya iby'Umucyo, ngo atume bose bizera. 
1:8 Icyakora uwo si we uwo Mucyo, ahubwo ni we wahamije ibyawo. 
1:9 Uwo Mucyo ni we Mucyo nyakuri, kandi ubwo ni bwo yatangiraga kuza mu isi ngo amurikire umuntu wese.
1:10 Yari mu isi ndetse ni we wayiremye, nyamara ab'isi ntibamumenya. 
1:11 Yaje mu bye, ariko abe ntibamwemera. 
1:12 Icyakora abamwemeye bose bakizera izina rye, yabahaye ubushobozi bwo kuba abana b'Imana. 
1:13 Abo ntibabyawe n'amaraso cyangwa n'ubushake bw'umubiri, cyangwa n'ubushake bw'umugabo, ahubwo babyawe n'Imana.
1:14 Jambo uwo yabaye umuntu abana natwe (tubona ubwiza bwe busa n'ubw'Umwana w'ikinege wa Se), yuzuye ubuntu n'ukuri.
1:15 Yohana yahamije iby'uwo avuga yeruye ati “Uwo ni we navuze nti ‘Uzaza hanyuma ni we unduta, kuko yahozeho ntarabaho.’ ”
1:16 Kandi ibimwuzuye akaba ari byo twahaweho twese, ni ubuntu bukurikira ubundi, 
1:17 kuko amategeko yatanzwe na Mose, ariko ubuntu n'ukuri byo byazanywe na Yesu Kristo. 
1:18 Uhereye kera kose nta muntu wigeze kubona Imana, ahubwo Umwana w'ikinege uri mu gituza cya Se, ni we wayimenyekanishije.
1:19 Ibi ni byo Yohana yahamije, ubwo Abayuda bamutumagaho abatambyi n'Abalewi, bavanywe i Yerusalemu no kumubaza bati “Uri nde?”
1:20 Nuko ntiyabahisha ukuri, ahubwo araberurira ati “Si jye Kristo.”
1:21   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Guteg 18.15,18; Mal 3.23  
1:22 Baramubaza bati “None se uri nde ngo dusubize abadutumye? Wowe wiyita nde?”
1:23   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Yes 40.3  
1:24 Abari batumwe bari Abafarisayo. 
1:25 Nuko baramubaza bati “None ubatiriza iki, ko utari Kristo, ntube na Eliya, ntube na wa muhanuzi?”
1:26 Yohana arabasubiza ati “Jye ndabatirisha amazi, ariko muri mwe hahagaze uwo mutaramenya, 
1:27 uwo ni we unsimbura kandi ntibinkwiriye gupfundura udushumi tw'inkweto ze.”
1:28 Ibyo byabereye i Betaniya hakurya ya Yorodani, aho Yohana yabatirizaga.
1:29 Bukeye bw'aho abona Yesu aza aho ari aravuga ati “Nguyu Umwana w'intama w'Imana, ukuraho ibyaha by'abari mu isi. 
1:30 Uyu ni we navuze nti ‘Nyuma yanjye hazaza umugabo unduta ubukuru, kuko yahozeho ntarabaho.’ 
1:31 Icyakora sinari muzi, ariko kugira ngo yerekwe Abisirayeli, ni cyo cyatumye nza mbatirisha amazi.”
1:32 Kandi Yohana arahamya ati “Nabonye Umwuka amanuka ava mu ijuru asa n'inuma, atinda kuri we. 
1:33 Icyakora sinari muzi, keretse yuko Iyantumye kubatirisha amazi yambwiye iti ‘Uwo uzabona Umwuka amanukira akagwa kuri we, uwo ni we ubatirisha Umwuka Wera’. 
1:34 Nanjye mbibonye, mpamya yuko ari Umwana w'Imana.”
1:35 Bukeye bw'aho, Yohana yongera guhagararana n'abigishwa be babiri. 
1:36 Yitegereza Yesu agenda aravuga ati “Nguyu Umwana w'intama w'Imana.”
1:37 Abo bigishwa bombi bumvise avuze atyo, bakurikira Yesu. 
1:38 Yesu arahindukira abona bamukurikiye arababaza ati “Murashaka iki?” Baramusubiza bati “Rabi, (risobanurwa ngo: Mwigisha) ucumbitse he?” 
1:39 Arababwira ati “Nimuze murahabona.” Barajyana babona aho acumbitse. Hari nk'isaha cumi, baherako bamarana na we umwanya burīra.
1:40 Andereya mwene se wa Simoni Petero, yari umwe muri abo babiri bumvise Yohana bagakurikira Yesu. 
1:41 Abanza kubona mwene se Simoni aramubwira ati “Twabonye Mesiya” (risobanurwa ngo: Kristo). 
1:42 Amuzanira Yesu, na we aramwitegereza aramubwira ati “Uri Simoni mwene Yona, uzitwa Kefa.” (Risobanurwa ngo: ibuye).
1:43 Bukeye bwaho Yesu ashaka kujya i Galilaya. Abona Filipo aramubwira ati “Nkurikira.” 
1:44 Filipo uwo yari uw'i Betsayida, umudugudu w'iwabo wa Andereya na Petero. 
1:45 Filipo abona Natanayeli aramubwira ati “Uwo Mose yanditse mu mategeko, n'abahanuzi bakamwandika twamubonye. Ni Yesu mwene Yosefu w'i Nazareti.”
1:46 Natanayeli aramubaza ati “Mbese i Nazareti hari icyiza cyahaturuka?” Filipo aramusubiza ati “Ngwino urebe.”
1:47 Yesu abona Natanayeli aza aho ari amuvugaho ati “Dore Umwisirayeli nyakuri, udafite uburiganya.”
1:48 Natanayeli aramubaza ati “Wamenyeye he?” Yesu aramusubiza ati “Filipo ataraguhamagara, ubwo wari munsi y'umutini nakubonye.”
1:49 Natanayeli aramusubiza ati “Rabi, uri Umwana w'Imana koko. Ni wowe Mwami w'Abisirayeli.”
1:50 Yesu aramusubiza ati “Mbese wijejwe n'uko nkubwiye yuko nakubonye uri munsi y'umutini? Uzabona ibiruta ibyo.” 
1:51  Kandi arongera aramubwira ati “Ni ukuri, ni ukuri, ndababwira yuko muzabona ijuru rikingutse, abamarayika b'Imana bazamuka bavuye ku Mwana w'umuntu, bakamumanukiraho.”
2:1 Ku munsi wa gatatu hacyujijwe ubukwe i Kana y'i Galilaya, kandi na nyina wa Yesu yari ahari. 
2:2 Yesu bamutorana n'abigishwa be ngo batahe ubwo bukwe. 
2:3 Nuko vino ishize, nyina wa Yesu aramubwira ati “Nta vino bafite.”
2:4 Yesu aramubwira ati “Mubyeyi, tubigendanyemo dute? Igihe cyanjye ntikiragera.”
2:5 Nyina abwira abahereza ati “Icyo ababwira cyose mugikore.”
2:6 Hariho intango esheshatu zaremwe mu mabuye, zashyiriweho kwiyeza nk'uko umugenzo w'Abayuda wari uri, intango yose irimo incuro ebyiri cyangwa eshatu z'amazi. 
2:7 Yesu arababwira ati “Mwuzuze intango amazi.” Barazuzuza bageza ku ngara. 
2:8 Arababwira ati “Nimudahe noneho mushyire umusangwa mukuru.” Barayamushyīra. 
2:9 Uwo musangwa mukuru asogongeye amazi ahindutse vino ntiyamenya aho iturutse, keretse ba bahereza badashye amazi ni bo bari babizi. Umusangwa mukuru ahamagara umukwe 
2:10 aramubwira ati “Abandi bose babanza vino nziza, abantu bamara guhaga bakabona kuzana izitaryoshye, ariko wowe ho washyinguye inziza aba ari zo uherutsa.”
2:11 Icyo ni cyo kimenyetso cya mbere Yesu yakoreye i Kana y'i Galilaya, yerekana icyubahiro cye, abigishwa be baramwizera.
2:12   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Mat 4.13  
2:13   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Kuva 12.1-27  
2:14 Ageze mu rusengero asangamo abahatundira inka n'intama n'inuma, n'abandi bicaye bavunja ifeza. 
2:15 Abohekanya imigozi ayigira nk'ikiboko, bose abirukana n'intama n'inka mu rusengero, amena ifeza z'abaguraga inuma 
2:16 ati “Nimukureho bino, mureke guhindura inzu ya Data iguriro.” 
2:17   
2:18 Abayuda baramubaza bati “Ubwo ugize utyo watwereka kimenyetso ki?”
2:19   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Mat 26.61; 27.40; Mar 14.58; 15.29  
2:20 Nuko Abayuda bati “Uru rusengero ko rwubatswe mu myaka mirongo ine n'itandatu, nawe ngo uzarwubaka mu minsi itatu?”
2:21 Ariko urusengero yavugaga ni umubiri we. 
2:22 Nuko azuwe abigishwa be bibuka ko yabivuze, bemera ibyanditswe na rya jambo Yesu yari yaravuze.
2:23 Nuko ubwo yari i Yerusalemu mu minsi mikuru ya Pasika, abantu benshi babonye ibimenyetso akora bizera izina rye, 
2:24 ariko Yesu ntiyabiringira kuko yari azi abantu bose. 
2:25 Ntiyagombaga kubwirwa iby'abantu, kuko ubwe yari azi ibibarimo.
3:1 Hariho umuntu wo mu Bafarisayo witwaga Nikodemo, umutware wo mu Bayuda. 
3:2 Uwo yasanze Yesu nijoro aramubwira ati “Mwigisha, tuzi yuko uri umwigisha wavuye ku Mana, kuko ari nta wubasha gukora ibimenyetso ujya ukora, keretse Imana iri kumwe na we.”
3:3 Yesu aramusubiza ati “Ni ukuri, ni ukuri, ndakubwira yuko umuntu utabyawe ubwa kabiri, atabasha kubona ubwami bw'Imana.”
3:4 Nikodemo aramubaza ati “Mbese umuntu yabasha ate kubyarwa akuze? Yakongera agasubira mu nda ya nyina akabyarwa?”
3:5 Yesu aramusubiza ati “Ni ukuri, ni ukuri, ndakubwira yuko umuntu utabyawe n'amazi n'Umwuka atabasha kwinjira mu bwami bw'Imana. 
3:6 Ikibyarwa n'umubiri na cyo ni umubiri, n'ikibyarwa n'Umwuka na cyo ni umwuka. 
3:7 Witangazwa n'uko nkubwiye yuko bibakwiriye kubyarwa ubwa kabiri. 
3:8 Umuyaga uhuha aho ushaka, ukumva guhuha kwawo ariko ntumenya aho uva cyangwa aho ujya. Ni ko uwabyawe n'Umwuka wese amera.”
3:9 Nikodemo aramusubiza ati “Ibyo byashoboka bite?” 
3:10 Yesu aramusubiza ati “Ukaba uri umwigisha w'Abisirayeli ntumenye ibyo! 
3:11 Ni ukuri, ni ukuri, ndakubwira yuko tuvuga ibyo tuzi kandi duhamya ibyo twabonye, nyamara ntimwemera ibyo duhamya. 
3:12 Ubwo nababwiye iby'isi ntimwemere, nimbabwira iby'ijuru muzemera mute? 
3:13 Ntawazamutse ngo ajye mu ijuru, keretse Umwana w'umuntu wavuye mu ijuru, akamanuka akaza hasi.
3:14   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Kub 21.9  
3:15 kugira ngo umwizera wese abone guhabwa ubugingo buhoraho.”
3:16 Kuko Imana yakunze abari mu isi cyane, byatumye itanga Umwana wayo w'ikinege kugira ngo umwizera wese atarimbuka, ahubwo ahabwe ubugingo buhoraho. 
3:17 Kuko Imana itatumye Umwana wayo mu isi gucira abari mu isi ho iteka, ahubwo yabikoreye kugira ngo abari mu isi bakizwe na we.
3:18 Umwizera ntacirwaho iteka, utamwizera amaze kuricirwaho kuko atizeye izina ry'Umwana w'Imana w'ikinege. 
3:19 Uko gucirwaho iteka ni uku: ni uko umucyo waje mu isi, abantu bagakunda umwijima kuwurutisha umucyo babitewe n'uko ibyo bakora ari bibi, 
3:20 kuko umuntu wese ukora ibibi yanga umucyo, kandi ntaza mu mucyo ngo ibyo akora bitamenyekana, 
3:21 ariko ukora iby'ukuri ni we uza mu mucyo, ngo ibyo akora bigaragare ko byakorewe mu Mana.
3:22 Hanyuma y'ibyo Yesu ajyana n'abigishwa be mu gihugu cy'i Yudaya, atindanayo na bo abatiza abantu. 
3:23 Ariko Yohana we</span><span class="note f"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body"><span class="fk">Ariko Yohana we: </span><span class="ft"> cyangwa, Yohana na we.
3:24   
3:25 Abigishwa ba Yohana bajya impaka n'Umuyuda ku byo kwiyeza. 
3:26 Basanga Yohana baramubwira bati “Mwigisha, uwari kumwe nawe hakurya ya Yorodani, uwo wahamyaga dore na we arabatiza, n'abantu bose baramusanga.”
3:27 Yohana arabasubiza ati “Nta cyo umuntu yashobora kwiha ubwe, keretse yagihawe kivuye mu ijuru. 
3:28  Namwe murambere abagabo yuko navuze nti ‘Si jye Kristo, ahubwo natumwe kumubanziriza.’ 
3:29 Uwo umugeni asanga ni we mukwe, kandi umuranga iyo ahagaze iruhande rw'umukwe amwumva anezezwa n'ijwi rye. None uwo munezero wanjye mwinshi cyane urasohoye. 
3:30 Uwo akwiriye gukuzwa, naho jye nkwiriye kwicisha bugufi.”
3:31 Uwavuye mu ijuru ni we usumba byose, naho uwo mu isi we ni uw'isi nyine, kandi n'ibyo avuga ni iby'isi. Uwavuye mu ijuru ni we usumba byose, 
3:32 kandi ibyo yabonye n'ibyo yumvise ni byo ahamya, nyamara nta wemera ibyo ahamya. 
3:33 Uwemera ibyo ahamya, aba yemeye n'uko n'Imana ari inyakuri. 
3:34 Uwatumwe n'Imana avuga amagambo yayo, kuko Imana idatanga Umwuka imugeze. 
3:35  Se akunda Umwana we kandi yamweguriye byose, 
3:36 uwizera uwo Mwana aba abonye ubugingo buhoraho, ariko utumvira uwo Mwana ntazabona ubugingo, ahubwo umujinya w'Imana uguma kuri we.
4:1 Nuko Umwami Yesu amenya yuko Abafarisayo bumvise ko yigisha kandi abatiza benshi, arusha Yohana, 
4:2 (icyakora Yesu ubwe si we wabatizaga, ahubwo ni abigishwa be), 
4:3 ni cyo cyatumye ava i Yudaya agasubira i Galilaya, 
4:4 yiyumvamo ko akwiriye kunyura i Samariya.
4:5   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Itang 33.19; Yos 24.32  
4:6 kandi aho hari iriba rya Yakobo. Nuko Yesu ananijwe n'uko yagenze cyane apfa kwicara kuri iryo riba, hari nk'isaha esheshatu.
4:7 Umusamariyakazi aza kuvoma, Yesu aramubwira ati “Mpa utuzi two kunywa”, 
4:8 (kuko abigishwa be bari bagiye mu mudugudu kugura ibyo kurya.)
4:9   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Ezira 4.1-5; Neh 3.33-34  
4:10 Yesu aramusubiza ati “Iyaba wari uzi impano y'Imana, ukamenya n'ugusabye amazi uwo ari we, nawe uba umusabye na we akaguha amazi y'ubugingo.”
4:11 Undi ati “Databuja, ko udafite icyo uvomesha n'iriba rikaba ari rirerire, none se ayo mazi y'ubugingo wayakura he? 
4:12 Mbese ye uruta sogokuruza Yakobo wadufukuriye iri riba, kandi akaba yaranywaga amazi yaryo ubwe n'abana be n'amatungo ye?”
4:13 Yesu aramusubiza ati “Umuntu wese unywa aya mazi azongera kugira inyota, 
4:14 ariko unywa amazi nzamuha ntazagira inyota rwose iteka ryose, ahubwo amazi nzamuha azamuhindukiramo isoko y'amazi adudubiza kugeza mu bugingo buhoraho.”
4:15 Umugore aramubwira ati “Databuja, mpa kuri ayo mazi ntazagira inyota, kandi ntazagaruka kuvoma hano kuko ari kure.”
4:16 Yesu aramubwira ati “Genda uhamagare umugabo wawe maze ugaruke hano.”
4:17 Umugore aramusubiza ati “Nta mugabo mfite.”
4:18 kuko wari ufite abagabo batanu, n'uwo ufite ubu si uwawe. Ibyo byo ubivuze ukuri.”
4:19 Umugore aramubwira ati “Databuja, menye yuko uri umuhanuzi. 
4:20 Ba sogokuruza bacu basengeraga kuri uyu musozi, namwe mukagira ngo i Yerusalemu ni ho hakwiriye gusengerwa.”
4:21 Yesu aramusubiza ati“Mugore, nyizera. Igihe kizaza, ubwo bazaba batagisengera Data kuri uyu musozi cyangwa i Yerusalemu. 
4:22 Dore mwebweho musenga icyo mutazi, ariko twebwe dusenga ibyo tuzi kuko agakiza kava mu Bayuda. 
4:23 Ariko igihe kiraje ndetse kirasohoye, ubwo abasenga by'ukuri basengera Data mu Mwuka no mu kuri, kuko Data ashaka ko bene abo ari bo bamusenga. 
4:24 Imana ni Umwuka, n'abayisenga bakwiriye kuyisengera mu Mwuka no mu kuri.”
4:25 Umugore aramubwira ati “Nzi yuko Mesiya azaza, ari we witwa Kristo, kandi ubwo azaza azatubwira byose.”
4:26 Yesu aramubwira ati “Ni jye tuvugana.”
4:27 Uwo mwanya abigishwa be baraza batangazwa n'uko avugana n'uwo mugore, ariko ntihagira umubaza ati “Urashaka iki?” Cyangwa ati “Ni iki gitumye uvugana na we?”
4:28 Nuko uwo mugore asiga ikibindi cye, aragenda ajya mu mudugudu abwira abantu ati 
4:29 “Nimuze murebe umuntu umbwiye ibyo nakoze byose, murebe ahari ko ari Kristo!” 
4:30 Bava mu mudugudu ngo baze aho ari.
4:31 Batarahagera abigishwa be baramwinginga bati “Mwigisha, akira ufungure.”
4:32 Arababwira ati “Mfite ibyokurya mutazi.”
4:33 Abigishwa be barabazanya bati “Mbese hari uwamuzaniye ibyokurya?”
4:34 Yesu arababwira ati “Ibyokurya byanjye ni ugukora ibyo uwantumye ashaka, no kurangiza umurimo we. 
4:35 Mbese ntimuvuga ngo ‘Hasigaye amezi ane isarura rigasohora?’ Dore ndababwira, nimwubure amaso murebe imirima yuko imaze kwera ngo isarurwe. 
4:36 Umusaruzi ahabwe ibihembo, ateranirize imyaka ubugingo buhoraho ngo umubibyi n'umusaruzi banezeranwe, 
4:37 kuko iri jambo ari iry'ukuri ngo ‘Habiba umwe, hagasarura undi.’ 
4:38 Nabatumye gusarura ibyo mutahinze, abandi barakoze namwe mwazunguye umurimo wabo.”
4:39 Nuko benshi mu Basamariya bo muri uwo mudugudu bizera Yesu, kuko bumvise amagambo y'uwo mugore ahamya ati “Yambwiye ibyo nakoze byose.” 
4:40 Nuko Abasamariya bamusanze baramwinginga ngo agumane na bo, asibirayo kabiri.
4:41 Hizera abandi benshi baruta aba mbere, kuko biyumviye ijambo rye. 
4:42 Maze babwira uwo mugore bati “Noneho si amagambo yawe yonyine aduteye kwizera, kuko natwe twiyumviye tukamenya ko uyu ari we Mukiza w'abari mu isi koko.”
4:43 Iyo minsi ibiri ishize, avayo ajya i Galilaya, 
4:44  kuko Yesu yahamije yuko umuhanuzi atagira icyubahiro mu gihugu cy'iwabo. 
4:45   
4:46   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Yoh 2.1-11  
4:47 Yumvise yuko Yesu avuye i Yudaya asohoye i Galilaya aramusanga, amwingingira kumanuka ngo akize umwana we kuko yendaga gupfa. 
4:48 Yesu aramubwira ati “Ntimwakwizera keretse mubonye ibimenyetso n'ibitangaza.”
4:49 Uwo mutware aramusubiza ati “Databuja, manuka akana kanjye katarapfa.”
4:50 Yesu aramubwira ati “Genda, umwana wawe ni muzima.”
4:51   </span><span class="it"><span class="content">Bukeye bwaho
4:52 Ababaza igihe yoroherewe baramusubiza bati “Ejo ku isaha ndwi, ni ho ubuganga bwamuvuyemo.”
4:53 Nuko se amenya yuko ari yo saha Yesu yamubwiriyemo ati “Umwana wawe ni muzima.” Nuko uwo mutware aramwizera ubwe n'ab'inzu ye bose.
4:54 Icyo ni cyo kimenyetso cya kabiri Yesu yakoze, avuye i Yudaya ageze i Galilaya.
5:1 Hanyuma y'ibyo haba iminsi mikuru y'Abayuda, nuko Yesu ajya i Yerusalemu. 
5:2 Kandi i Yerusalemu bugufi bw'irembo ry'intama hariho ikidendezi, mu Ruheburayo kitwa Betesida, cyariho amabaraza atanu. 
5:3 Muri ayo mabaraza hari abarwayi benshi, barimo impumyi n'ibirema n'abanyunyutse, [bari bategereje ko amazi yihinduriza, 
5:4 kuko rimwe na rimwe marayika yamanukaga akajya muri icyo kidendezi, agahinduriza amazi. Nuko umuntu wabanzaga kujyamo amazi yihindurije, ni we wakiraga indwara ye iyo ari yo yose.]
5:5 Hariho umuntu wari ufite indwara, ayimaranye imyaka mirongo itatu n'umunani. 
5:6 Yesu amubonye aryamye amenya yuko amaze igihe kirekire arwaye, aramubaza ati “Mbese urashaka gukira?”
5:7 Umurwayi aramusubiza ati “Databuja, simfite umuntu unjugunya mu kidendezi iyo amazi yihindurije, nkīza undi antanga kumanukamo.”
5:8 Yesu aramubwira ati “Byuka wikorere uburiri bwawe ugende.” 
5:9 Muri ako kanya uwo muntu arakira, yikorera uburiri bwe aragenda.
5:10   
5:11 Na we arabasubiza ati “Uwankijije ni we wambwiye ati ‘Ikorere uburiri bwawe ugende.’ ”
5:12 Baramubaza bati “Uwo muntu ni nde wakubwiye ngo wikorere ugende?”
5:13 Ariko uwakijijwe ntiyamenya uwo ari we, kuko Yesu yari yigendeye kandi hari abantu benshi.
5:14 Hanyuma y'ibyo Yesu amubona mu rusengero aramubwira ati “Dore ubaye muzima, ntukongere gukora icyaha utazabona ishyano riruta irya mbere.”
5:15 Uwo muntu aragenda abwira Abayuda yuko ari Yesu wamukijije. 
5:16 Ni cyo cyatumaga Abayuda bashaka kurenganya Yesu, kuko yakoraga bene nk'ibyo ku isabato. 
5:17 Ariko arabasubiza ati “Data arakora kugeza n'ubu, nanjye ndakora.”
5:18 Ni cyo cyatumye Abayuda barushaho gushaka kumwica, kuko uretse kuzirura isabato gusa, ahubwo ahora yita n'Imana ko ari Se bwite, akīgereranya na yo.
5:19 Yesu arabasubiza ati “Ni ukuri, ni ukuri, ndababwira yuko ari nta cyo Umwana abasha gukora ubwe atabonye Se agikora, kuko ibyo Se akora byose n'Umwana ari byo akora, 
5:20 kuko Se akunda Umwana we akamwereka ibyo akora byose, ndetse azamwereka n'imirimo iruta iyi kugira ngo mutangare. 
5:21 Nk'uko Se azura abapfuye akabaha ubugingo, ni ko n'Umwana aha ubugingo abo ashaka. 
5:22 Kuko ari nta n'umwe Data aciraho iteka, ahubwo yabihaye Umwana ngo abe ari we uca amateka yose, 
5:23 kugira ngo abantu bose bubahe Umwana nk'uko bubaha Se. Utubaha uwo Mwana ntaba yubashye na Se wamutumye.
5:24 “Ni ukuri, ni ukuri, ndababwira yuko uwumva ijambo ryanjye akizera uwantumye, aba afite ubugingo buhoraho kandi ntazacirwaho iteka, ahubwo aba avuye mu rupfu ageze mu bugingo. 
5:25 Ni ukuri, ni ukuri, ndababwira yuko igihe kije ndetse kirasohoye, ubwo abapfa bumva kandi bazumva ijwi ry'Umwana w'Imana, n'abaryumvise bazaba bazima, 
5:26 kuko nk'uko Data afite ubugingo muri we, ni ko yabuhaye Umwana ngo abugire na we. 
5:27 Kandi yamuhaye ubutware bwo guca amateka, kuko ari Umwana w'umuntu. 
5:28 Ntimutangazwe n'ibyo kuko igihe kizaza, ubwo abari mu bituro bose bazumva ijwi rye 
5:29   
5:30 “Nta cyo mbasha gukora ubwanjye, ahubwo uko numvise ni ko nca amateka, kandi ayo nca ni ay'ukuri kuko ntakurikiza ibyo nkunda ubwanjye, ahubwo nkurikiza ibyo uwantumye akunda.
5:31 “Nakwihamya ubwanjye, guhamya kwanjye ntikuba ari uk'ukuri, 
5:32 ahubwo hariho undi umpamya, nanjye nzi yuko ibyo ampamya ari iby'ukuri. 
5:33  Mwatumye kuri Yohana, na we yahamije ukuri. 
5:34 Icyakora sinishingikirije ku buhamya bw'umuntu, ahubwo mbivugiye kugira ngo mukizwe. 
5:35 Uwo yari itabaza ryaka rimurika, namwe mwamaze igihe gito mwishimira umucyo we. 
5:36 Ariko mfite ibimpamya biruta ibya Yohana, kuko imirimo Data yampaye ngo nyisohoze, iyo mirimo nkora ari yo impamya ubwayo yuko Data ari we wantumye. 
5:37  Kandi Data wantumye na we yahamije ibyanjye ubwe. Ntimwigeze kumva ijwi rye, habe no kubona ishusho ye, 
5:38 ndetse ntimufite n'ijambo rye riguma muri mwe, kuko uwo yatumye mutamwizeye. 
5:39 Murondora mu byanditswe, kuko mwibwira ko muri byo arimo mufite ubugingo buhoraho, kandi ari byo bimpamya. 
5:40 Nyamara mwanze kuza aho ndi, ngo muhabwe ubugingo.
5:41 “Sinshaka ishimwe ry'abantu, 
5:42 ariko mwebwe ndabazi yuko mudakunda Imana mu mitima yanyu. 
5:43 Jye naje mu izina rya Data ntimwanyemera, ariko undi naza mu izina rye ubwe we muzamwemera. 
5:44 Mbese mwabasha mute kwizera kandi mumaranira gushimwa n'abantu, mu cyimbo cyo gushaka ishimwe riva ku Mana ubwayo? 
5:45 Mwe gutekereza yuko nzabarega kuri Data kuko hariho ubarega, ndetse ni Mose uwo mwiringiye. 
5:46 Iyo mwizera Mose nanjye muba munyizeye, kuko ari ibyanjye yanditse. 
5:47 Ariko se nimutizera ibyo uwo yanditse, noneho n'amagambo yanjye muzayizera mute?”
6:1 Hanyuma y'ibyo Yesu ajya hakurya y'Inyanja y'i Galilaya, ari yo yitwa Tiberiya. 
6:2 Iteraniro ry'abantu benshi riramukurikira, kuko babonye ibimenyetso yakoreye abarwayi. 
6:3 Yesu azamuka umusozi yicaranayo n'abigishwa be. 
6:4 Ubwo Pasika, iminsi mikuru y'Abayuda, yendaga gusohora. 
6:5 Yesu yubura amaso, abonye abantu benshi baza aho ari abaza Filipo ati “Turagura hehe ibyokurya ngo aba babone ibyo barya?” 
6:6 Icyatumye amubaza atyo yagira ngo amugerageze, ubwe yari azi icyo ari bukore.
6:7 Filipo aramusubiza ati “Imitsima yagurwa idenariyo magana abiri ntiyabakwira, nubwo umuntu yaryaho gato.”
6:8 Umwe mu bigishwa be, ari we Andereya mwene se wa Simoni Petero aramubwira ati 
6:9 “Hano hari umuhungu ufite imitsima itanu y'ingano, n'ifi ebyiri. Ariko ibyo byamarira iki abantu bangana batya?”
6:10 Yesu ati “Nimwicaze abantu.” Aho hantu hari ubwatsi bwinshi, nuko abagabo baricara, bari nk'ibihumbi bitanu. 
6:11 Yesu yenda ya mitsima arayishimira ayigabanya abicaye, n'ifi na zo azigenza atyo nk'uko bazishakaga. 
6:12 Bamaze guhaga abwira abigishwa be ati “Nimuteranye ubuvungukira busigaye hatagira ikintu gipfa ubusa.” 
6:13 Barateranya buzuza intonga cumi n'ebyiri z'ubuvungukira bwa ya mitsima itanu y'ingano, ubwo abariye bashigaje.
6:14 Abantu babonye ikimenyetso yakoze baravuga bati “Ni ukuri uyu ni we wa muhanuzi wari ukwiriye kuza mu isi.” 
6:15 Yesu amenye yuko bagiye kuza kumufata ngo bamwimike, arabiyufūra asubira ku musozi wenyine.
6:16 Bugorobye abigishwa be baramanuka bajya ku nyanja. 
6:17 Bikira mu bwato, bambuka inyanja bagana i Kaperinawumu. Bwari bwije kandi na Yesu atarabageraho, 
6:18 inyanja ihindurizwa n'umuyaga mwinshi uhuha. 
6:19 Bamaze kuvugama sitadiyo makumyabiri n'eshanu cyangwa mirongo itatu, babona Yesu agendesha amaguru hejuru y'inyanja. Ageze bugufi bw'ubwato baratinya. 
6:20 Ariko arababwira ati “Ni jye; mwitinya.” 
6:21 Baherako bemera ko ajya mu bwato, uwo mwanya bugera imusozi aho bajyaga.
6:22 Bukeye bwaho iteraniro ry'abantu benshi ryari rihagaze hakurya y'inyanja, bamenya yuko hari ubwato bumwe gusa kandi ko Yesu atīkiranye n'abigishwa be muri bwo, ahubwo ko bagiye bonyine ubwabo. 
6:23 Nuko ayandi mato avuye i Tiberiya amaze kwambuka, afata bugufi bw'aho barīriye ya mitsima, Umwami Yesu amaze kuyishimira. 
6:24 Nuko abo bantu babonye ko Yesu n'abigishwa be badahari, bikira muri ayo mato ubwabo bajya i Kaperinawumu kumushakirayo.
6:25 Bamubonye hakurya y'inyanja baramubaza bati “Mwigisha, waje hano ryari?”
6:26 Yesu arabasubiza ati “Ni ukuri, ni ukuri, ndababwira yuko ibimenyetso mwabonye atari byo bituma munshaka, ahubwo ni ya mitsima mwariye mugahaga. 
6:27 Ntimukorere ibyokurya bishira, ahubwo mukorere ibyokurya bigumaho kugeza ku bugingo buhoraho, ibyo Umwana w'umuntu azabaha, kuko Se ari we Mana yamushyizeho ikimenyetso cyayo.”
6:28 Baramubaza bati “Tugire dute ngo dukore imirimo y'Imana?”
6:29 Arabasubiza ati “Umurimo w'Imana nguyu: ni uko mwizera uwo yatumye.”
6:30 Baramubaza bati “Urakora kimenyetso ki ngo tukirebe tukwizere? Icyo wakora ni iki? 
6:31   
6:32 Yesu arababwira ati “Ni ukuri, ni ukuri, ndababwira yuko Mose atari we wabahaye umutsima uvuye mu ijuru, ahubwo ni Data ubaha umutsima w'ukuri uvuye mu ijuru. 
6:33 Kuko umutsima w'Imana ari umanuka uva mu ijuru, ugaha abari mu isi ubugingo.”
6:34 Baramubwira bati “Databuja, ujye uduha uwo mutsima iteka.”
6:35 Yesu arababwira ati “Ni jye mutsima w'ubugingo, uza aho ndi ntazasonza na hato, n'unyizera ntabwo azagira inyota na hato. 
6:36 Ariko nababwiye yuko mwambonye, nyamara ntimwizera. 
6:37 Uwo Data yampaye wese aza aho ndi, kandi uza aho ndi sinzamwirukana na hato. 
6:38 Kuko ntavanywe mu ijuru no gukora ibyo nishakiye, ahubwo nazanywe no gukora ibyo uwantumye ashaka, 
6:39 kandi ibyo uwantumye ashaka ni ibi: ni ukugira ngo mu byo yampaye byose ntagira na kimwe nzimiza, ahubwo ngo nzakizure ku munsi w'imperuka. 
6:40 Kuko icyo Data ashaka ari iki: ni ukugira ngo umuntu wese witegereza Umwana akamwizera ahabwe ubugingo buhoraho, nanjye nzamuzure ku munsi w'imperuka.”
6:41 Nuko Abayuda baramwitotombera kuko yavuze ati “Ni jye mutsima wavuye mu ijuru.” 
6:42 Bati “Uyu si we Yesu mwene Yosefu, ntituzi se na nyina? Ni iki gituma avuga ko yavuye mu ijuru?”
6:43 Yesu arabasubiza ati “Mwe kwitotomba. 
6:44 Nta wubasha kuza aho ndi, keretse arehejwe na Data wantumye, nanjye nkazamuzura ku munsi w'imperuka. 
6:45  Byanditswe mu byahanuwe ngo ‘Bose bazigishwa n'Imana.’ Umuntu wese wumvise ibya Data akabyiga aza aho ndi. 
6:46 Si ukugira ngo hari umuntu wabonye Data, keretse uwavuye ku Mana, uwo ni we wabonye Data. 
6:47 Ni ukuri, ni ukuri, ndababwira yuko uwizera ari we ufite ubugingo buhoraho. 
6:48 Ni jye mutsima w'ubugingo. 
6:49 Ba sekuruza wanyu barīraga manu mu butayu, nyamara barapfuye. 
6:50 Uyu ni wo mutsima umanuka uva mu ijuru, kugira ngo umuntu uwurya ye gupfa. 
6:51 Ni jye mutsima muzima wavuye mu ijuru. Umuntu narya uwo mutsima azabaho iteka ryose, kandi umutsima nzatanga ku bw'abari mu isi kugira ngo babone ubugingo, ni umubiri wanjye.”
6:52 Abayuda bajya impaka bati “Mbese uyu yabasha ate kuduha umubiri we ngo tuwurye?”
6:53 Yesu arababwira ati “Ni ukuri, ni ukuri, ndababwira yuko nimutarya umubiri w'Umwana w'umuntu, ntimunywe n'amaraso ye, nta bugingo muba mufite muri mwe. 
6:54 Urya umubiri wanjye, akanywa amaraso yanjye aba afite ubugingo buhoraho, nanjye nzamuzura ku munsi w'imperuka, 
6:55 kuko umubiri wanjye ari ibyokurya by'ukuri, n'amaraso yanjye ari ibyokunywa by'ukuri. 
6:56 Urya umubiri wanjye, akanywa amaraso yanjye, aguma muri jye nanjye nkaguma muri we. 
6:57 Nk'uko Data uhoraho yantumye, nanjye nkaba ndiho ku bwa Data, ni ko undya na we azabaho ku bwanjye. 
6:58 Uyu ni wo mutsima wavuye mu ijuru, si nk'uwo ba sekuruza banyu bariye bagapfa, ahubwo urya uyu mutsima azabaho iteka ryose.”
6:59 Ibyo yabivugiye mu isinagogi, yigishiriza i Kaperinawumu.
6:60 Nuko benshi mu bigishwa be babyumvise baravuga bati “Iryo jambo rirakomeye, ushobora kuryihanganira ni nde?”
6:61 Yesu amenya mu mutima we yuko abigishwa be babyitotombeye, arababaza ati “Mbese ibyo bibabereye igisitaza? 
6:62 None mwabona Umwana w'umuntu azamuka ajya aho yahoze mbere byamera bite? 
6:63 Umwuka ni we utanga ubugingo, umubiri nta cyo umaze. Amagambo mbabwiye ni yo mwuka, kandi ni yo bugingo, 
6:64 ariko hariho bamwe muri mwe batizera.” (Kuko uhereye mbere na mbere Yesu yari azi abatizera abo ari bo, n'uzamugambanira uwo ari we.) 
6:65 Nuko aravuga ati “Ni cyo cyatumye mbabwira yuko hatariho ubasha kuza aho ndi, keretse abihawe na Data.”
6:66 Benshi mu bigishwa be bahera ubwo basubira inyuma, barorera kugendana na we. 
6:67 Yesu abaza abigishwa be cumi na babiri ati “Kandi namwe murashaka kugenda?”
6:68   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Mat 16.16; Mar 8.29; Luka 9.20  
6:69 natwe tukaba twizeye tuzi yuko uri Kristo, Uwera w'Imana?”
6:70 Yesu arabasubiza ati “Mbese si jye wabitoranyirije uko muri cumi na babiri? None dore umwe muri mwe ni umwanzi.” 
6:71 Uwo yavugaga ni Yuda Isikariyota mwene Simoni kuko ari we wari ugiye kuzamugambanira, ari umwe muri abo cumi na babiri.
7:1 Hanyuma y'ibyo Yesu aba i Galilaya, ntiyashakaga kuba i Yudaya, kuko Abayuda bashakaga kumwica. 
7:2  Iminsi mikuru y'Abayuda yitwa Ingando yendaga gusohora. 
7:3 Nuko bene se baramubwira bati “Va hano ujye i Yudaya, kugira ngo abigishwa bawe barebe imirimo ukora, 
7:4 kuko ari nta muntu ushaka kumenyekana wakorera ikintu mu rwihisho. Kuko ukora iyo mirimo, ngaho genda wiyereke abari mu isi bose!” 
7:5 (Bene se babivugiye batyo kuko batamwizeraga).
7:6 Yesu arababwira ati “Igihe cyanjye ntikirasohora, ariko igihe cyanyu gihoraho iteka. 
7:7 Ab'isi ntibabasha kubanga, ariko jyewe baranyanga kuko mpamya ibyabo, yuko imirimo yabo ari mibi. 
7:8 Mwebweho nimujye muri iyo minsi mikuru, ariko jyeweho sinjyayo ubu kuko igihe cyanjye kitarasohora.” 
7:9 Amaze kubabwira ibyo, asigara i Galilaya.
7:10 Ariko bene se bamaze kwikubura bagiye mu minsi mikuru, na we aragenda ariko atari ku mugaragaro, ahubwo nko mu rwihisho. 
7:11 Abayuda bamushakira muri ya minsi mikuru bati “Mbese wa wundi ari he?”
7:12 Abantu bamugira impaka cyane, bamwe bati “Ni umuntu mwiza”, abandi bati “Oya, ayobya abantu.” 
7:13 Ariko ntihagira umuvuga ku mugaragaro, kuko batinyaga Abayuda.
7:14 Iminsi mikuru igeze hagati, Yesu azamuka ajya mu rusengero arigisha. 
7:15 Abayuda baratangara bati “Uyu yakuye hehe ubu bwenge ko atigishijwe?”
7:16 Yesu arabasubiza ati “Ibyo nigisha si ibyanjye, ahubwo ni iby'Iyantumye. 
7:17 Umuntu nashaka gukora ibyo Ikunda, azamenya ibyo nigisha ko byavuye ku Mana, cyangwa yuko mbivuga ku bwanjye. 
7:18 Uvuga ibye ubwe aba yishakiye icyubahiro, ariko ushakira Iyamutumye icyubahiro uwo ni we w'ukuri, gukiranirwa ntikuri muri we. 
7:19 Mbese Mose ntiyabahaye amategeko? Ariko muri mwe nta wuyumvira. Murashakira iki kunyica?”
7:20 Abantu baramusubiza bati “Ufite dayimoni. Ni nde ushaka kukwica?”
7:21 Yesu arabasubiza ati “Nakoze umurimo umwe, namwe mwese murawutangarira. 
7:22  Mose yabahaye umuhango wo gukeba, (icyakora ntiwakomotse kuri Mose, ahubwo wakomotse kuri ba sokuruza banyu), ndetse mukeba abantu no ku isabato. 
7:23  Ubwo umuntu akebwa ku isabato ngo amategeko ya Mose atazirurwa, none kuki mundakarira kuko nakijije umubiri w'umuntu wose ku isabato? 
7:24 Mwe guca imanza ku bigaragara gusa, ahubwo muce imanza z'ukuri.”
7:25 Nuko bamwe mu b'i Yerusalemu barabazanya bati “Uwo bashaka kwica si uyu? 
7:26 Nyamara dore aravugira ku mugaragaro ko ari nta cyo bamugira! Mbese harya, ni ukuri koko abakuru bacu bemeye ko uyu ari we Kristo? 
7:27 Uyu tuzi aho yaturutse, ariko Kristo naza nta wuzamenya aho yaturutse.”
7:28 Nuko Yesu avuga cyane yigishiriza mu rusengero ati “Jyewe muranzi n'aho naturutse murahazi, ariko sinaje ku bwanjye, ahubwo Iyantumye ni iy'ukuri, iyo mutazi. 
7:29 Nyamara jyewe ndayizi kuko navuye kuri yo, kandi ari yo yantumye.”
7:30 Nuko bashaka kumufata ariko ntihagira ubihangara, kuko igihe cye cyari kitarasohora. 
7:31 Nuko abantu benshi mu bahateraniye baramwizera bati “Harya Kristo naza, mugira ngo azakora ibimenyetso byinshi biruta ibyo uyu yakoze?”
7:32 Abafarisayo bumva ibyo rubanda bamuvugira mu byongorerano, nuko abatambyi bakuru n'Abafarisayo batuma abasirikare ngo bamufate.
7:33 Yesu aherako aravuga ati “Hasigaye umwanya muto nkiri kumwe namwe, hanyuma nkajya ku wantumye. 
7:34 Muzanshaka mwe kumbona, kandi aho nzaba ndi ntimubasha kujyayo.”
7:35 Nuko Abayuda baravugana bati “Mbese uyu agiye kujya he, aho tutazamubona? Aho ntagiye kujya mu batataniye mu Bagiriki akaba ari bo yigisha? 
7:36 Iryo jambo avuze ni iriki ngo ‘Muzanshaka mwe kumbona’, kandi ngo ‘Aho nzaba ndi ntimubasha kujyayo?’ ”
7:37   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Lewi 23.36  
7:38  Unyizera, imigezi y'amazi y'ubugingo izatemba iva mu nda ye, nk'uko ibyanditswe bivuga.” 
7:39 Ibyo yabivuze yerekeje ku Mwuka Wera, uwo abamwizera bendaga guhabwa, ariko ubwo Umwuka yari ataraza kuko Yesu yari atarahabwa ubwiza bwe.
7:40 Bamwe muri rubanda bumvise ayo magambo baravuga bati “Ni ukuri uyu ni we wa muhanuzi.”
7:41 Abandi bati “Uyu ni we Kristo.” Ariko abandi bati “Mbese Kristo aturuka i Galilaya? 
7:42  Ibyanditswe ntibivuga ngo Kristo azakomoka mu rubyaro rwa Dawidi, aturuke i Betelehemu, ikirorero Dawidi yarimo?” 
7:43 Nuko abantu baramupfa. 
7:44 Bamwe muri bo bashaka kumufata ariko ntihagira n'umukoza urutoki.
7:45 Nuko ba basirikare basubira ku batambyi bakuru n'Abafarisayo. Na bo barababaza bati “Mubujijwe n'iki kumuzana?”
7:46 Abasirikare barabasubiza bati “Yemwe, ntabwo higeze kuba umuntu uvuga nka we.”
7:47 Abafarisayo barabasubiza bati “Mbese namwe mwayobejwe? 
7:48 Hari umuntu n'umwe wo mu bakuru cyangwa mu Bafarisayo wamwizeye? 
7:49 Ariko abo bantu batazi amategeko baravumwe.”
7:50   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Yoh 3.1-2  
7:51 “Mbese amategeko yacu acira umuntu urubanza, batabanje kumwumva no kumenya ibyo yakoze?”
7:52 Baramusubiza bati “Mbega nawe waturutse i Galilaya? Irebere mu byanditswe, urasanga ko nta muhanuzi uturuka i Galilaya.”
7:53 Barataha, umuntu wese ajya iwe.
