8:14 Yesu arabasubiza ati “Nubwo nihamya ibyo nihamya ni iby'ukuri, kuko nzi aho naturutse n'aho njya. Ariko mwebweho ntimuzi aho naturutse cyangwa aho njya. 
8:15 Muca urubanza nk'abantu, ariko jyeweho nta n'umwe ncira urubanza. 
8:16 Ariko naho naca urubanza, urwo naca ruba ari urw'ukuri kuko ntari jyenyine, ahubwo ndi kumwe na Data wantumye. 
8:17 Kandi no mu mategeko yanyu, handitswe ngo ibyo abantu babiri bahamya ni iby'ukuri. 
8:18 Ndihamya ubwanjye, na Data wantumye na we arampamya.”
8:19 Baramubaza bati “So ari hehe?”
8:20 Ayo magambo yayababwiriye mu ruturiro ubwo yigishirizaga mu rusengero, nyamara ntihagira umufata kuko igihe cye cyari kitarasohora.
8:21 Nuko yongera kubabwira ati “Ndagenda kandi muzanshaka, nyamara muzapfana ibyaha byanyu. Aho njya ntimubasha kujyayo.”
8:22 Abayuda barabazanya bati “Mbese aziyahura? Kuko avuze ati ‘Aho njya ntimubasha kujyayo.’ ”
8:23 Arababwira ati “Mwebwe mukomoka hasi, jyewe nkomoka hejuru. Mwebwe muri ab'iy'isi, ariko jyewe sindi uw'iy'isi. 
8:24 Ni cyo gitumye mbabwira yuko muzapfana ibyaha byanyu, kuko nimutizera ko ndi We, muzapfana ibyaha byanyu.”
8:25 Baramubaza bati “Uri nde?”
