12:17 Nuko ba bantu bari kumwe na we, ubwo yahamagaraga Lazaro ngo ave mu gituro akamuzura, bamubera abahamya. 
12:18 Kandi ni cyo cyatumye abantu benshi bajya kumusanganira, kuko bumvise ko yakoze icyo kimenyetso. 
12:19 Nuko Abafarisayo baravugana bati “Murarora yuko murushywa n'ubusa, dore rubanda rwose ruramukurikiye.”
12:20 Hariho Abagiriki mu baje gusenga mu minsi mikuru, 
12:21 basanga Filipo w'i Betsayida y'i Galilaya, baramwinginga bati “Mutware, turashaka kureba Yesu.”
12:22 Filipo araza abibwira Andereya, Andereya na Filipo na bo baraza babibwira Yesu. 
12:23 Yesu arabasubiza ati “Igihe kirasohoye ngo Umwana w'umuntu ahabwe ubwiza bwe. 
12:24 Ni ukuri, ni ukuri, ndababwira yuko iyo akabuto k'ishaka kataguye hasi ngo gapfe kagumaho konyine, ariko iyo gapfuye kera imbuto nyinshi. 
12:25  Ukunda ubugingo bwe arabubura, ariko uwanga ubugingo bwe muri iyi si, azaburinda ageze ku bugingo buhoraho. 
12:26 Umuntu nankorera ankurikire, kuko aho ndi n'umugaragu wanjye ari ho azaba. Umuntu nankorera Data azamuha icyubahiro.
12:27 “None umutima wanjye urahagaze, kandi navuga iki? Nti ‘Data, nkiza undokore iki gihe’, kandi ari byo byanzanye ngo nkigeremo? 
12:28 Data, ubahiriza izina ryawe.”
12:29 Abantu bahagaze aho baryumvise baravuga bati “Ni inkuba.” Abandi bati “Ni marayika uvuganye na we.”
12:30 Yesu arabasubiza ati “Iryo jwi ntirije ku bwanjye, rije ku bwanyu. 
12:31 Ubu urubanza rw'ab'isi rurasohoye, ubu umutware w'ab'iyi si abaye igicibwa. 
12:32 Nanjye nimanikwa hejuru y'isi, nzireherezaho abantu bose.” 
12:33 Ibyo yabivugiye kugaragaza urupfu yendaga gupfa urwo ari rwo.
12:34   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Zab 110.4; Yes 9.6; Ezek 37.25; Dan 7.14  
12:35 Yesu arababwira ati “Hasigaye umwanya muto, umucyo ukiri muri mwe. Nimugende mugifite umucyo butabiriraho mukiri mu nzira, kuko ugenda mu mwijima atamenya iyo ajya. 
12:36 Mwizere umucyo mugifite umucyo, kugira ngo mube abana b'umucyo.”
12:37 Nubwo yakoreye ibimenyetso byinshi bingana bityo imbere yabo ntibamwizeye, 
12:38   
12:39 Ni cyo cyatumye badashobora kwizera, kuko Yesaya yongeye kuvuga ati
12:40   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Yes 6.10  
12:41 Ibyo byavuzwe na Yesaya, kuko yabonye ubwiza bwa Yesu akamuvuga.
12:42 Nyamara mu batware na bo benshi baramwizeye, ariko ku bw'Abafarisayo ntibabyerura ngo badacibwa mu isinagogi, 
12:43 kuko bakundaga gushimwa n'abantu kuruta gushimwa n'Imana.
12:44 Yesu aravuga cyane ati “Unyizera si jye aba yizeye, ahubwo aba yizeye uwantumye, 
12:45 numbonye aba abonye uwantumye. 
12:46 Naje mu isi ndi umucyo, kugira ngo unyizera wese ataguma mu mwijima. 
12:47 Ariko umuntu niyumva amagambo yanjye ntayitondere, si jye umuciriyeho iteka, kuko ntazanywe no gucira abari mu isi ho iteka, ahubwo naje kubakiza. 
12:48 Unyanga ntiyemere amagambo yanjye afite umuciraho iteka. Ijambo navuze ni ryo rizamuciraho iteka ku munsi w'imperuka. 
12:49 Sinabivuze ku bwanjye, ahubwo Data wantumye ni we wantegetse ibyo nkwiriye kuvuga, n'ibyo nkwiriye kwigisha. 
12:50 Nanjye nzi yuko itegeko rye ari ryo bugingo buhoraho. Nuko rero ibyo mvuga, mbivuga uko Data yabimbwiye.”
13:1 Umunsi wa Pasika utarasohora, Yesu amenya yuko igihe cye gisohoye cyo kuva mu isi agasubira kuri Se. Urukundo yakunze abe bari mu isi, ni rwo yakomeje kubakunda kugeza imperuka.
13:2 Bakirya ibyokurya bya nijoro, Satani yari yamaze koshya umutima wa Yuda Isikariyota mwene Simoni ngo amugambanire. 
13:3 Yesu amenye ko Se amweguriye byose, kandi ko yavuye ku Mana kandi ko asubira kuri yo, 
13:4 ahaguruka aho yarīraga yiyambura umwitero, yenda igitambaro aragikenyeza. 
13:5 Aherako asuka amazi ku mbehe, atangira koza ibirenge by'abigishwa no kubihanaguza igitambaro akenyeje. 
13:6 Nuko yegera Simoni Petero na we aramubaza ati “Databuja, ni wowe unyoza ibirenge?”
13:7 Yesu aramusubiza ati “Ibyo nkora ubu ntubizi, ariko uzabimenya hanyuma.”
13:8 Petero aramubwira ati “Reka! Ntabwo nzemera na hato ko unyoza ibirenge.”
13:9 Simoni Petero aramubwira ati “Databuja, noneho ntunyoze ibirenge byonyine, ahubwo unyuhagire n'amaboko, umese n'umutwe.”
13:10 Yesu aramubwira ati “Uwuhagiwe nta kindi agomba keretse kōga ibirenge ngo abe aboneye rwose. Namwe muraboneye, ariko si mwese.” 
13:11 Icyatumye avuga ati “Ntimuboneye mwese”, ni uko yari azi uri bumugambanire uwo ari we.
13:12   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Luka 22.27  
13:13 Munyita Shobuja n'Umwigisha, ibyo mubivuga neza kuko ari ko ndi koko. 
13:14 Nuko rero, ubwo mbogeje ibirenge kandi ndi Shobuja n'Umwigisha, ni ko namwe mukwiriye kubyozanya. 
13:15 Mbahaye icyitegererezo, kugira ngo mukore nk'uko mbakoreye. 
13:16  Ni ukuri, ni ukuri, ndababwira yuko umugaragu ataruta shebuja, kandi intumwa itaruta uwayitumye. 
13:17 Nimumenye ibyo, murahirwa niba mubikora.
13:18   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Zab 41.10  
13:19 Dore ubu mbibabwiye bitari byaba, kugira ngo nibiba muzizere ko ndi We. 
13:20   
13:21 Yesu amaze kuvuga atyo, ahagarika umutima arahamya ati “Ni ukuri, ni ukuri, ndababwira yuko umwe muri mwe ari bungambanire.”
13:22 Abigishwa bararebana, kuko batari bazi uwo avuze uwo ari we. 
13:23 Hariho umwe mu bigishwa be, wari wiseguye igituza cya Yesu bafungura. Uwo ni wa wundi Yesu yakundaga. 
13:24 Simoni Petero aramurembuza aramubaza ati “Umubaze uwo avuze uwo ari we.”
13:25 Uwo ahengamira inyuma aho yari ari mu gituza cya Yesu, aramubaza ati “Databuja, ni nde?”
13:26 Yesu aramusubiza ati “Uwo ndi bukoreze inogo nkayimuha, ni we uwo.” Nuko akojeje inogo, arayenda ayiha Yuda Isikariyota mwene Simoni. 
13:27 Hanyuma yo guhabwa iyo nogo, ni bwo Satani yamwinjiyemo. Nuko Yesu aramubwira ati “Icyo ukora gikore vuba.” 
13:28 Ariko nta n'umwe wo mu bari bicaye basangira na we, wamenye icyatumye amubwira atyo. 
13:29 Kuko Yuda yari afite umufuka w'impiya, ni cyo cyatumye bamwe bakeka yuko Yesu yamubwiye ati “Genda ugure ibyo dushaka kurya ku munsi mukuru”, cyangwa ati “Gira icyo uha abakene.”
13:30 Nuko Yuda amaze kwakira inogo, muri ako kanya arasohoka kandi hari nijoro.
13:31 Amaze gusohoka Yesu aravuga ati “Noneho Umwana w'umuntu arubahirijwe, kandi Imana na yo yubahirijwe muri we. 
13:32 Kandi Imana ubwo yubahirijwe muri we, na yo izamwubahiriza muri yo ubwayo, kandi izamwubahiriza vuba. 
13:33  Bana bato, ndacyari hamwe namwe umwanya muto. Muzanshaka, kandi uko nabwiye Abayuda nti ‘Aho njya ntimubasha kuhajya’, namwe ni ko mbibabwira ubu. 
13:34  Ndabaha itegeko rishya ngo mukundane nk'uko nabakunze, mube ari ko namwe mukundana. 
13:35 Ibyo ni byo bose bazabamenyeraho ko muri abigishwa banjye, nimukundana.”
13:36 Simoni Petero aramubaza ati “Databuja, urajya he?”
13:37 Petero aramusubiza ati “Databuja, icyambuza kugukurikira ubu ni ik, ko nzanagupfira?”
13:38 Yesu aramusubiza ati “Uzampfira? Ni ukuri, ni ukuri, ndakubwira yuko inkoko itaza kubika, utaranyihakana gatatu.
14:1 “Ntimuhagarike imitima yanyu, mwizere Imana nanjye munyizere. 
14:2 Mu rugo rwa Data harimo amazu menshi: iyaba adahari mba mbabwiye, kuko ngiye kubategurira ahanyu. 
14:3 Kandi ubwo ngiye kubategurira ahanyu, nzagaruka mbajyane iwanjye, ngo aho ndi namwe muzabeyo. 
14:4 Kandi aho njya, inzira murayizi.”
14:5 Toma aramubwira ati “Databuja, ntituzi aho ujya, inzira twayibwirwa n'iki?”
14:6 Yesu aramubwira ati “Ni jye nzira n'ukuri n'ubugingo: nta wujya kwa Data ntamujyanye. 
14:7 Iyaba mwaramenye, muba mwaramenye na Data. Uhereye none muramuzi kandi mwamurebye.”
14:8 Filipo aramubwira ati “Databuja, twereke Data wa twese biraba bihagije.”
14:9 Yesu aramubaza ati “Nabanye namwe iminsi ingana ityo, kandi ntiwari wamenya, Filipo? Umbonye aba abonye Data. Ni iki gitumye uvuga uti ‘Twereke Data wa twese’? 
14:10 Ntiwizeye yuko ndi muri Data, na Data akaba ari muri jye? Amagambo mbabwira sinyavuga ku bwanjye, ahubwo Data uguma muri jye ni we ukora imirimo ye. 
14:11 Nimunyizere mwemere ko ndi muri Data, na Data akaba muri jye, ariko rero nimutizezwa n'ibyo mvuga, munyizezwe n'imirimo nkora ubwayo. 
14:12 Ni ukuri, ni ukuri, ndababwira yuko unyizera, imirimo nkora na we azayikora ndetse azakora n'iyiruta, kuko njya kwa Data. 
14:13 Kandi icyo muzasaba cyose mu izina ryanjye, nzagikorera kugira ngo Data yubahirizwe mu Mwana we. 
14:14 Nimugira icyo musaba cyose mu izina ryanjye nzagikora.
14:15 “Nimunkunda muzitondera amategeko yanjye. 
14:16 Nanjye nzasaba Data, na we azabaha undi Mufasha wo kubana namwe ibihe byose, 
14:17 ni we Mwuka w'ukuri. Ntibishoboka ko ab'isi bamuhabwa, kuko batamurora kandi batamuzi, ariko mwebweho muramuzi kuko abana namwe, kandi azaba muri mwe.
14:18 “Sinzabasiga nk'impfubyi, ahubwo nzaza aho muri. 
14:19 Hasigaye umwanya muto ab'isi ntibabe bakimbona, ariko mwebweho muzambona, kuko ndiho namwe muzabaho. 
14:20 Uwo munsi muzamenya ko ndi muri Data namwe mukaba muri jye, nanjye nkaba muri mwe.
14:21 “Ufite amategeko yanjye akayitondera ni we unkunda, kandi unkunda azakundwa na Data, nanjye nzamukunda mwiyereke.”
14:22 Yuda utari Isikariyota aramubaza ati “Databuja, bibaye bite ko ugiye kutwiyereka ntiwiyereke ab'isi?”
14:23 Yesu aramusubiza ati “Umuntu nankunda azitondera ijambo ryanjye, na Data azamukunda, tuzaza aho ari tugumane na we. 
14:24 Ariko utankunda ntiyitondera amagambo yanjye, kandi iryo jambo mwumvise si iryanjye, ahubwo ni irya Data wantumye.
14:25 “Ibyo mbibabwiye nkiri kumwe namwe, 
14:26 ariko Umufasha ari we Mwuka Wera, uwo Data azatuma mu izina ryanjye ni we uzabigisha byose, abibutse ibyo nababwiye byose.
14:27 “Mbasigiye amahoro, amahoro yanjye ndayabahaye. Icyakora simbaha nk'uko ab'isi batanga. Imitima yanyu ntihagarare kandi ntitinye. 
14:28 Mwumvise uko nababwiye nti ‘Ndagenda kandi nzagaruka aho muri.’ Iyaba mwankundaga, muba munejejwe n'uko njya kwa Data kuko Data anduta. 
14:29 Nuko rero mbibabwiye bitaraba, ngo ubwo bizaba muzizere. 
14:30 Sinkivugana namwe byinshi, kuko umutware w'ab'iyi si aza kandi nta cyo amfiteho, 
14:31 ahubwo nkora uko Data yantegetse, kugira ngo ab'isi bamenye ko munkunda.
15:1 “Ndi umuzabibu w'ukuri, kandi Data ni nyirawo uwuhingira. 
15:2 Ishami ryose ryo muri jye ritera imbuto arikuraho, iryera imbuto ryose aryanganyaho amahage yaryo ngo rirusheho kwera imbuto. 
15:3 None mumaze kwezwa n'ijambo nababwiye. 
15:4 Mugume muri jye, nanjye ngume muri mwe. Nk'uko ishami ritabasha kwera imbuto ubwaryo ritagumye mu muzabibu, ni ko namwe mutabibasha nimutaguma muri jye.
15:5 “Ni jye muzabibu, namwe muri amashami. Uguma muri jye nanjye nkaguma muri we, uwo ni we wera imbuto nyinshi, kuko ari nta cyo mubasha gukora mutamfite. 
15:6 Umuntu utaguma muri jye ajugunywa hanze nk'ishami ryumye, maze bakayateranya bakayajugunya mu muriro agashya. 
15:7 Nimuguma muri jye amagambo yanjye akaguma muri mwe, musabe icyo mushaka cyose muzagihabwa. 
15:8 Ibyo ni byo byubahisha Data, ni uko mwera imbuto nyinshi, mukaba abigishwa banjye.
15:9 “Uko Data yankunze ni ko nanjye nabakunze. Nuko rero mugume mu rukundo rwanjye. 
15:10 Nimwitondera amategeko yanjye muzaguma mu rukundo rwanjye, nk'uko nanjye nitondeye amategeko ya Data nkaguma mu rukundo rwe.
15:11 “Ibyo mbibabwiriye kugira ngo umunezero wanjye ube muri mwe, kandi n'umunezero wanyu ube wuzuye. 
15:12  Ngiri itegeko ryanjye: mukundane nk'uko nabakunze. 
15:13 Nta wufite urukundo ruruta urw'umuntu upfira incuti ze. 
15:14 Muri incuti zanjye, nimukora ibyo mbategeka. 
15:15 Sinkibita abagaragu kuko umugaragu atazi ibyo shebuja akora, ahubwo mbise incuti kuko ibyo numvise kuri Data byose mbibamenyesheje. 
15:16 Si mwe mwantoranyije, ahubwo ni jye wabatoranyije kandi mbashyiriraho kugira ngo mugende mwere imbuto, imbuto zanyu zigumeho kugira ngo icyo muzasaba Data cyose mu izina ryanjye akibahe. 
15:17 Ibyo mbibategekeye kugira ngo mukundane.
15:18 “Ab'isi nibabanga, mumenye ko babanje kunyanga batarabanga. 
15:19 Iyo muba ab'isi, ab'isi baba babakunze. Ariko kuko mutari ab'isi, ahubwo nabatoranyije mu b'isi, ni cyo gituma ab'isi babanga. 
15:20  Mwibuke ijambo nababwiye nti ‘Umugaragu ntaruta shebuja.’ Niba bandenganyije namwe bazabarenganya, niba bitondeye ijambo ryanjye, n'iryanyu na ryo bazaryitondera. 
15:21 Ariko ibyo byose bazabibagirira babahora izina ryanjye, kuko batazi Uwantumye uwo ari we. 
15:22 Iyaba ntaje ngo mvugane na bo ntibaba bafite icyaha, ariko noneho ntibafite uko biregura icyaha cyabo. 
15:23 Unyanga aba yanze na Data. 
15:24 Iyaba ntakoreye muri bo imirimo itakozwe n'undi muntu, nta cyaha baba bafite. Ariko noneho barayibonye, nyamara baratwanga jyewe na Data. 
15:25   
15:26 “Umufasha naza, uwo nzaboherereza ava kuri Data, ari we Mwuka w'ukuri ukomoka kuri Data, azampamya. 
15:27 Kandi namwe muzampamya, kuko uhereye mbere na mbere mwari kumwe nanjye.
16:1 “Icyo mbabwiriye ibyo ni ukugira ngo hatagira ikibagusha. 
16:2 Bazabaca mu masinagogi, kandi igihe kigiye kuza, uzabica wese azibwira ko akoreye Imana umurimo. 
16:3 Kandi ibyo bazabikorera batyo kuko batamenye Data, nanjye ntibamenye. 
16:4 Ariko ibyo mbibabwiriye kugira ngo igihe cyabyo nikigera, muzibuke ko ari jye wabibabwiye.
16:5 Ariko none ndajya ku Uwantumye, kandi muri mwe nta wumbaza ati ‘Urajya he?’ 
16:6 Ariko kuko mbabwiye ibyo, imitima yanyu yuzuye agahinda.
16:7 “Ariko ndababwira ukuri yuko ikizagira icyo kibamarira ari uko ngenda, kuko nintagenda Umufasha atazaza aho muri, ariko ningenda nzamuboherereza. 
16:8 Ubwo azaza azatsinda ab'isi, abemeze iby'icyaha n'ibyo gukiranuka n'iby'amateka; 
16:9 iby'icyaha, kuko batanyizeye, 
16:10 n'ibyo gukiranuka kuko njya kwa Data, kandi namwe muzaba mutakimbona, 
16:11 n'iby'amateka kuko umutware w'ab'iyi si aciriweho iteka.
16:12 “Ndacyafite ibyo kubabwira byinshi, ariko ubu ntimubasha kubyihanganira. 
16:13 Uwo Mwuka w'ukuri naza azabayobora mu kuri kose kuko atazavuga ku bwe, ahubwo ibyo azumva ni byo azavuga, kandi azababwira ibyenda kubaho. 
16:14 Uwo azanyubahiriza, kuko azenda ku byanjye akabibabwira. 
16:15 Ibyo Data afite byose ni ibyanjye, ni cyo gitumye mvuga nti ‘Azenda ku byanjye abibabwire.’
16:16 “Hasigaye igihe gito ntimumbone, maze hazabaho ikindi gihe gito mumbone.”
16:17 Bamwe mu bigishwa be barabazanya bati “Ibyo atubwiye ni ibiki ngo ‘Hasigaye igihe gito ntimumbone, maze hazabaho igihe gito mumbone’, kandi ngo ‘Kuko njya kuri Data.’ ” 
16:18 Kandi bati “Ibyo ni ibiki ngo ‘Igihe gito’? Ntituzi ibyo avuze.”
16:19 Yesu amenye ko bashaka kumubaza arababaza ati “Murabazanya ibyo mbabwiye ibyo ngo ‘Hasigaye igihe gito ntimumbone, maze hazabaho ikindi gihe gito mumbone’? 
16:20 Ni ukuri, ni ukuri, ndababwira yuko mwebweho muzarira mukaboroga, ariko ab'isi bazanezerwa. Mwebweho muzababara, ariko umubabaro wanyu uzahinduka umunezero. 
16:21 Umugore iyo aramukwa arababara kuko igihe cye gisohoye, ariko iyo umwana amaze kuvuka ntaba akibuka kuribwa, kuko anejejwe n'uko umuntu avutse mu isi. 
16:22 Ni ko namwe mubabara none, ariko nzongera kubonana namwe kandi imitima yanyu izanezerwa, n'umunezero wanyu nta muntu uzawubaka. 
16:23 Uwo munsi nta cyo muzambaza. Ni ukuri, ni ukuri, ndababwira yuko icyo muzasaba Data cyose mu izina ryanjye azakibaha. 
16:24 Kugeza none nta cyo mwasabye mu izina ryanjye. Musabe muzahabwa ngo umunezero wanyu ube wuzuye.
16:25 “Ibyo mbibabwiriye mu migani, ariko igihe kizaza sinzavuganira namwe mu migani, ahubwo nzababwira ibya Data neruye. 
16:26 Uwo munsi muzasaba mu izina ryanjye, kandi simbabwira ko nzabasabira kuri Data, 
16:27 kuko Data na we abakunda ubwe kuko mwankunze mukizera yuko navuye ku Mana. 
16:28 Navuye kuri Data nza mu isi, kandi isi ndayivamo nsubire kuri Data.”
16:29 Abigishwa baravuga bati “Dore noneho ureruye, nta mugani uduciriye. 
16:30 Ubu tuzi yuko uzi byose kandi ko utagomba ko umuntu wese agira icyo akubaza, ni cyo gituma twizera ko wavuye ku Mana.”
16:31 Yesu arabasubiza ati “None murizeye? 
16:32 Dore igihe kirenda gusohora ndetse kirasohoye, ubwo muri butatane umuntu wese ukwe, mukansiga jyenyine. Ariko sindi jyenyine, kuko Data ari kumwe nanjye. 
16:33 Ibyo mbibabwiriye kugira ngo mugire amahoro muri jye. Mu isi mugira umubabaro, ariko nimuhumure nanesheje isi.”
17:1 Yesu amaze kuvuga ibyo, yubura amaso areba mu ijuru ati “Data, igihe kirasohoye, ubahiriza Umwana wawe ngo Umwana akūbahishe, 
17:2 nk'uko wamuhaye ubutware ku bantu bose, kugira ngo abo wamuhaye bose abahe ubugingo buhoraho. 
17:3 Ubu ni bwo bugingo buhoraho, ko bakumenya ko ari wowe Mana y'ukuri yonyine, bakamenya n'uwo watumye ari we Yesu Kristo. 
17:4 Nakūbahishije mu isi, kuko narangije umurimo wampaye gukora. 
17:5 Na none Data, imbere yawe unyubahirishe cya cyubahiro nahoranye ndi kumwe nawe isi itararemwa.
17:6 “Abo wampaye mu isi mbamenyesheje izina ryawe. Bari abawe urabampa, none dore bitondeye ijambo ryawe. 
17:7 None bamenye yuko ibyo wampaye byose byaturutse kuri wowe, 
17:8 kuko amagambo wampaye nayabahaye na bo bakayemera, bakamenya by'ukuri ko naturutse kuri wowe, bakizera kandi ko ari wowe wantumye.
17:9 “Ndabasabira. Sinsabira ab'isi, ahubwo ndasabira abo wampaye kuko ari abawe, 
17:10 kandi ibyanjye byose ni ibyawe, n'ibyawe na byo ni ibyanjye kandi nubahirijwe muri bo. 
17:11 Jye sinkiri mu isi ariko bo bari mu isi, naho jye ndaza kuri wowe. Data Wera, ubarindire mu izina ryawe wampaye, ngo babe umwe nk'uko natwe turi umwe. 
17:12  Nkiri kumwe na bo, nabarindiraga mu izina ryawe wampaye. Narabarinze, muri bo nta muntu wabuze ngo arimbuke, keretse umwana wo kurimbuka ngo ibyanditswe bisohore. 
17:13 Ariko none ndaza kuri wowe, kandi ibyo mbivuze nkiri mu isi, ngo bagire umunezero wanjye wuzure muri bo. 
17:14 Nabahaye ijambo ryawe, kandi ab'isi barabanga kuko atari ab'isi, nk'uko nanjye ntari uw'isi. 
17:15 Sinsaba ko ubakura mu isi, ahubwo ubarinde Umubi. 
17:16 Si ab'isi nk'uko nanjye ntari uw'isi. 
17:17 Ubereshe ukuri: ijambo ryawe ni ryo kuri. 
17:18 Uko wantumye mu isi nanjye ni ko nabatumye mu isi, 
17:19 kandi nanjye niyeza ku bwabo ngo na bo babe bereshejwe ukuri.
17:20 “Sinsabira aba bonyine, ahubwo ndasabira n'abazanyizezwa n'ijambo ryabo, 
17:21 ngo bose babe umwe nk'uko uri muri jye, Data, nanjye nkaba muri wowe ngo na bo babe umwe muri twe, ngo ab'isi bizere ko ari wowe wantumye. 
17:22 Nanjye mbahaye ubwiza wampaye, ngo babe umwe nk'uko natwe turi umwe. 
17:23 Jyewe mbe muri bo nawe ube muri jye, ngo babe umwe rwose, ngo ab'isi bamenye ko ari wowe wantumye, ukabakunda nk'uko wankunze.
17:24 “Data, abo wampaye ndashaka ko aho ndi na bo bahabana nanjye, ngo babone ubwiza bwanjye wampaye, kuko wankunze isi itararemwa. 
17:25 Data ukiranuka, ab'isi ntibakumenye ariko jyewe narakumenye, n'aba na bo bamenye ko ari wowe wantumye. 
17:26 Nabamenyesheje izina ryawe kandi nzaribamenyesha, ngo urukundo wankunze rube muri bo, nanjye mbe muri bo.”
18:1 Yesu amaze kuvuga ayo magambo asohokana n'abigishwa be, yambuka umugezi witwa Kidironi, hariho agashyamba akajyanamo n'abigishwa be. 
18:2 Kandi na Yuda umugambanira na we yari azi aho hantu, kuko Yesu yahajyanaga n'abigishwa be kenshi. 
18:3 Nuko Yuda amaze guhabwa ingabo z'abasirikare n'abagaragu b'abatambyi bakuru n'ab'Abafarisayo, ajyayo afite amatabaza n'imuri n'intwaro. 
18:4 Yesu amenye ibyenda kumubaho byose, arabasanganira arababaza ati “Murashaka nde?”
18:5 Baramusubiza bati “Ni Yesu w'i Nazareti.”
18:6 Amaze kubabwira ati “Ni jye”, bagenza imigongo bagwa hasi. 
18:7 Nuko yongera kubabaza ati “Murashaka nde?”
18:8 Yesu arabasubiza ati “Mbabwiye ko ari jye. Nuko rero niba ari jye mushaka mureke aba bagende.” 
18:9   
18:10 Nuko Simoni Petero yari afite inkota, arayikura ayikubita umugaragu w'umutambyi mukuru amuca ugutwi kw'iburyo. Uwo mugaragu yitwaga Maluko. 
18:11   
18:12 Nuko izo ngabo n'umutware wazo n'abagaragu b'Abayuda bafata Yesu baramuboha, 
18:13 babanza kumujyana kwa Ana kuko yari sebukwe wa Kayafa, wari umutambyi mukuru muri uwo mwaka. 
18:14   
18:15 Simoni Petero n'undi mwigishwa bakurikira Yesu. Uwo mwigishwa yari azwi n'umutambyi mukuru, yinjirana na Yesu mu rugo rw'umutambyi mukuru. 
18:16 Ariko Petero yari ahagaze hanze ku irembo. Wa mwigishwa wundi wari uzwi n'umutambyi mukuru, arasohoka avugana n'umuja ukumīra, nuko yinjiza Petero.
18:17 Uwo muja ukumīra abaza Petero ati “Mbese aho nawe nturi uwo mu bigishwa b'uriya muntu?”
18:18 Abagaragu n'abasirikare bari bahagaze aho, bacanye umuriro w'amakara kuko hari imbeho barota, na Petero na we yari kumwe na bo ahagaze yota.
18:19 Nuko umutambyi mukuru abaza Yesu iby'abigishwa be n'ibyo yigishaga. 
18:20 Yesu aramusubiza ati “Nigishaga ab'isi neruye, iteka nigishiriza mu masinagogi no mu rusengero aho Abayuda bose bateranira, nta cyo navuze rwihishwa. 
18:21 Urambariza iki? Abumvaga ba ari bo ubaza ibyo nababwiye, ni bo bazi ibyo navuze.”
18:22 Amaze kuvuga atyo, umwe mu basirikare wari uhagaze aho akubita Yesu urushyi ati “Uku ni ko usubiza umutambyi mukuru?”
18:23 Yesu aramusubiza ati “Niba mvuze ikibi kimpamye. Ariko niba ari neza umpoye iki?”
18:24 Nuko Ana amwohereza ari imbohe kuri Kayafa, umutambyi mukuru.
18:25 Ubwo Simoni Petero yari ahagaze yota. Baramubaza bati “Mbese nawe nturi uwo mu bigishwa be?”
18:26 Umwe mu bagaragu b'umutambyi mukuru, mwene wabo w'uwo Petero yaciye ugutwi aramubaza ati “Harya sinakubonye uri kumwe na we muri ka gashyamba?”
18:27 Petero yongera kubihakana, muri ako kanya inkoko irabika.
18:28 Bavana Yesu kwa Kayafa bamujyana mu rukiko, hari mu museke. Ubwabo ntibinjira mu rukiko ngo batihumanya, bakabura uko barya ibya Pasika. 
18:29 Nuko Pilato arasohoka ajya aho bari ati “Uyu muntu muramurega iki?”
18:30 Baramusubiza bati “Uyu iyaba atakoze icyaha ntituba tumukuzaniye.”
18:31 Pilato arababwira ati “Nimumujyane, abe ari mwe mumucira urubanza nk'uko amategeko yanyu ari.”
18:32   
18:33 Pilato yongera kwinjira mu rukiko, ahamagara Yesu aramubaza ati “Wowe uri umwami w'Abayuda?”
18:34 Yesu na we aramubaza ati “Mbese ibyo ubibajije ku bwawe, cyangwa se ni abandi bakubwiye ibyanjye?”
18:35 Pilato aramusubiza ati “Uragira ngo ndi Umuyuda? Ab'ubwoko bwanyu n'abatambyi bakuru ni bo bakunzaniye. Wakoze iki?”
18:36 Yesu aramusubiza ati “Ubwami bwanjye si ubw'iyi si, iyaba ubwami bwanjye bwari ubw'iyi si, abagaragu banjye baba barwanye ngo ntahabwa Abayuda, ariko noneho ubwami bwanjye si ubw'ino.”
18:37 Pilato aramubaza ati “Noneho ga uri umwami?”
18:38 Pilato aramubaza ati “Ukuri ni iki?”
18:39 Icyakora mufite umugenzo ko mbabohorera imbohe imwe mu minsi ya Pasika. Mbese murashaka ko mbabohorera umwami w'Abayuda?”
18:40 Ariko bongera gusakuza bati “Si we dushaka, ahubwo utubohorere Baraba.” Baraba uwo yari umwambuzi.
19:1 Nuko Pilato aherako ajyana Yesu, amukubita imikoba. 
19:2 Abasirikare baboha ikamba ry'amahwa barimwambika mu mutwe, bamwambika n'umwenda w'umuhengeri. 
19:3 Baramwegera baramubwira bati “Ni amahoro, Mwami w'Abayuda!” Bamukubita inshyi.
19:4 Pilato yongera gusohoka arababwira ati “Dore ndamusohoye, ndamubazaniye ngo mumenye yuko ari nta cyaha mubonyeho.” 
19:5 Nuko Yesu asohoka yambaye ikamba ry'amahwa n'umwenda w'umuhengeri, Pilato arababwira ati “Uwo muntu nguyu!”
19:6 Abatambyi bakuru n'abasirikare bamubonye batera hejuru bati “Mubambe! Mubambe!”
19:7 Abayuda baramusubiza bati “Dufite itegeko, ku bw'iryo tegeko akwiriye gupfa kuko yigize Umwana w'Imana.”
19:8 Pilato yumvise ibyo arushaho gutinya. 
19:9 Nuko yongera kwinjira mu rukiko maze abaza Yesu ati “Wavuye he?”
19:10 Pilato aramubaza ati “Uranyihorera? Ntuzi yuko mfite ububasha bwo kukurekura, kandi ko mfite ububasha bwo kukubamba?”
19:11 Yesu aramusubiza ati “Ntiwagira ububasha bwo kugira icyo untwara utabuhawe buvuye mu ijuru, ni cyo gituma ukungabije akurusha icyaha.”
19:12 Uhereye ubwo Pilato ashaka uburyo bwo kumurekura. Ariko Abayuda batera hejuru bati “Nurekura uyu uraba utari incuti ya Kayisari, kuko umuntu wese wigize umwami aba agomeye Kayisari.”
19:13 Nuko Pilato yumvise ibyo asohora Yesu, yicara ku ntebe y'imanza ahantu hitwa Amabuye ashashwe, mu Ruheburayo hitwa Gabata. 
19:14 (Ubwo hari ku munsi wo kwitegura ibya Pasika, hari nk'isaha esheshatu.) Nuko abwira Abayuda ati “Nguyu umwami wanyu.”
19:15 Na bo batera hejuru bati “Mukureho, mukureho umubambe!”
19:16 Aherako aramubaha ngo abambwe.
19:17 asohoka yiyikorereye umusaraba agera ahantu hitwa i Nyabihanga, mu Ruheburayo hitwa i Gologota. 
19:18 Bamubambanaho n'abandi babiri hirya no hino, Yesu ari hagati. 
19:19 Pilato yandika urwandiko arushyira ku musaraba, rwanditswe ngo “YESU W'I NAZARETI, UMWAMI W'ABAYUDA.” 
19:20 Urwo rwandiko benshi mu Bayuda bararusoma, kuko ahantu babambye Yesu hari bugufi bw'umurwa, kandi rwari rwanditswe mu Ruheburayo, no mu Ruroma, no mu Rugiriki. 
19:21 Nuko Abatambyi bakuru b'Abayuda babwira Pilato bati “Ntiwandike ngo ‘Umwami w'Abayuda’, ahubwo wandike uti ‘Yiyise umwami w'Abayuda.’ ”
19:22 Pilato arabasubiza ati “Icyo nanditse nacyanditse.”
19:23 Nuko abasirikare bamaze kubamba Yesu, bajyana imyambaro ye bayigabanyamo kane, umusirikare wese umugabane we, ariko hasigara ikanzu ye. Iyo kanzu ntiyari ifite umubariro, ahubwo yari iboshywe yose uhereye hejuru ukageza hasi. 
19:24   
19:25 Nyina wa Yesu na nyina wabo, na Mariya muka Kilopa na Mariya Magadalena, bari bahagaze ku musaraba wa Yesu. 
19:26 Nuko Yesu abonye nyina n'umwigishwa yakundaga ahagaze bugufi, abwira nyina ati “Mubyeyi, nguyu umwana wawe.”
19:27 Maze abwira uwo mwigishwa ati “Nguyu nyoko.” Uhereye uwo mwanya uwo mwigishwa amujyana iwe.
19:28   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Zab 69.22; 22.16  
19:29 Hari hateretse ikibindi cyuzuye vino isharira. Nuko benda sipongo yuzuye iyo vino isharira, bayishyira ku rubingo barayimusomesha. 
19:30 Yesu amaze gusoma iyo vino aravuga ati “Birarangiye.”
19:31 Uwo munsi wari uwo kwitegura Pasika, kandi Abayuda ntibashakaga ko imibiri iguma ku musaraba ku isabato, kuko iyo sabato yari umunsi mukuru, ni ko gusaba Pilato kubavuna amaguru ngo babamburwe. 
19:32 Abasirikare baraza babanza kuri umwe bamuvuna amaguru, n'undi wari ubambanywe na we bamugenza batyo, 
19:33 ariko bageze kuri Yesu basanga amaze gupfa ntibamuvuna amaguru, 
19:34 ariko umwe muri bo amucumita icumu mu rubavu, uwo mwanya havamo amaraso n'amazi. 
19:35 Uwabibonye ni we ubihamije, kandi ibyo ahamya ni iby'ukuri, kandi azi ko avuga ukuri ngo namwe mwizere. 
19:36  Kuko ibyo byabereyeho kugira ngo ibyanditswe bisohore ngo “Nta gufwa rye rizavunwa.” 
19:37   
19:38 Hanyuma y'ibyo haza Yosefu wo mu Arimataya, na we yari umwigishwa wa Yesu ariko rwihishwa, kuko yatinyaga Abayuda. Uwo ajya kwa Pilato amwaka intumbi ya Yesu ngo ayikureho, Pilato aramwemerera, araza akuraho intumbi ya Yesu. 
19:39  Na Nikodemo wa wundi wigeze kumusanga nijoro cya gihe, araza azanye ishangi ivanze n'umusaga, kuremera kwayo kwari nk'ibiro mirongo itanu. 
19:40 Bajyana intumbi ya Yesu bayizingira mu myenda y'ibitare hamwe n'iyo mibavu, nk'uko Abayuda bagenzaga bahamba. 
19:41 Aho hantu yabambwe hari agashyamba, kandi muri ako gashyamba hari imva nshya itarahambwamo umuntu. 
19:42 Aho ni ho bahambye Yesu, kuko wari umunsi wo kwitegura kw'Abayuda, kandi iyo mva yari iri hafi.
20:1 Ku wa mbere w'iminsi irindwi, mu rubungabungo hatarabona Mariya Magadalena aza ku gituro, asanga igitare gikuwe ku gituro. 
20:2 Arirukanka asanga Simoni Petero na wa mwigishwa wundi Yesu yakundaga arababwira ati “Bakuye Umwami Yesu mu gituro, kandi ntituzi aho bamushyize.”
20:3 Petero asohokana na wa mwigishwa wundi bajya ku gituro. 
20:4 Bombi birukira icyarimwe, ariko uwo mwigishwa asiga Petero aba ari we ubanza kugera ku gituro. 
20:5 Arunama arungurukamo, abona imyenda y'ibitare ishyizwe hasi ariko ntiyinjiramo. 
20:6 Maze Simoni Petero na we aza amukurikiye, yinjira mu gituro abona imyenda y'ibitare ishyizwe hasi, 
20:7 n'igitambaro cyari mu mutwe we kidashyizwe hamwe n'imyenda y'ibitare, ahubwo cyari kizinze kiri ukwacyo hirya. 
20:8 Ni cyo cyatumye na wa mwigishwa wundi wabanje kugera ku gituro na we yinjira. Abibonye yizera </span><span class="it"><span class="content">ibyo yabwiwe na wa mugore,
20:9 kuko bari bataramenya ibyanditswe ko akwiriye kuzuka. 
20:10 Maze abigishwa basubirayo bajya iwabo.
20:11 Ariko Mariya yari ahagaze ku gituro arira. Akirira arunama arunguruka mu gituro, 
20:12 abona abamarayika babiri bambaye imyenda yera bicaye, umwe ku musego n'undi ku mirambizo, aho intumbi ya Yesu yari yarashyizwe. 
20:13 Baramubaza bati “Mugore, urarizwa n'iki?”
20:14 Amaze kuvuga atyo arakebuka, abona Yesu ahagaze ariko ntiyamenya ko ari we. 
20:15 Yesu aramubaza ati “Mugore, urarizwa n'iki? Urashaka nde?”
20:16 Yesu aramubwira ati “Mariya.”
20:17 Yesu aramubwira ati “Ntunkoreho kuko ntarazamuka ngo njye kwa Data, ahubwo jya kubwira bene Data yuko nzamutse ngiye kwa Data ari we So, kandi ku Mana yanjye ari yo Mana yanyu.”
20:18 Mariya Magadalena aragenda, abarira abigishwa inkuru ati “Nabonye Umwami”, kandi abatekerereza ibyo yamubwiye.
20:19 Nuko kuri uwo munsi bugorobye, ari wo wa mbere w'iminsi irindwi, abigishwa bari bateraniye mu nzu, inzugi zikinze kuko batinyaga Abayuda. Yesu araza ahagarara hagati yabo arababwira ati “Amahoro abe muri mwe.” 
20:20 Amaze kuvuga atyo abereka ibiganza bye n'urubavu rwe. Abigishwa babonye Umwami baranezerwa. 
20:21 Yesu yongera kubabwira ati “Amahoro abe muri mwe. Uko Data yantumye ni ko nanjye mbatumye.” 
20:22 Amaze kuvuga atyo abahumekeraho ati “Nimwakire Umwuka Wera. 
20:23   
20:24 Ariko Toma umwe muri abo cumi na babiri witwaga Didumo, ntiyari kumwe na bo ubwo Yesu yazaga. 
20:25 Ni cyo cyatumye abandi bigishwa bamubwira bati “Tubonye Umwami!”
20:26 Nuko iminsi munani ishize, abigishwa bongera guterana mu nzu nka mbere na Toma ari kumwe na bo. Yesu araza abahagarara hagati, kandi inzugi zari zigikinze arababwira ati “Amahoro abe muri mwe.” 
20:27 Maze abwira Toma ati “Zana hano urutoki rwawe urebe ibiganza byanjye, kandi uzane n'ikiganza cyawe ugishyire mu rubavu rwanjye, kandi we kuba utizera ahubwo ube uwizeye.”
20:28 Toma aramusubiza ati “Mwami wanjye! Kandi Mana yanjye!”
20:29 Yesu aramubwira ati “Wijejwe n'uko umbonye, hahirwa abizeye batambonye.”
20:30 Hariho n'ibindi bimenyetso byinshi Yesu yakoreye imbere y'abigishwa, bitanditswe muri iki gitabo. 
20:31 Ariko ibi byandikiwe kugira ngo mwizere yuko Yesu ari Kristo Umwana w'Imana, kandi ngo nimwizera muherwa ubugingo mu izina rye.
21:1 Hanyuma y'ibyo Yesu yongera kwiyereka abigishwa be ku Nyanja ya Tiberiya, yiyerekana atya: 
21:2 Simoni Petero na Toma witwa Didumo, na Natanayeli w'i Kana y'i Galilaya, na bene Zebedayo n'abandi bigishwa babiri bari bari kumwe. 
21:3 Baramubwira bati “Natwe turajyana nawe.” Barahaguruka bīkira mu bwato, ariko bakesha iryo joro ari nta cyo bafashe. 
21:4 Umuseke umaze gutambika Yesu ahagarara mu kibaya cy'inyanja, ariko abigishwa ntibamenya ko ari we. 
21:5 Yesu arababaza ati “Yemwe bana banjye, mufite icyo kurya?”
21:6   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Luka 5.6  
21:7 Wa mwigishwa Yesu yakundaga abwira Petero ati “Ni Umwami Yesu.” Nuko Simoni Petero yumvise ko ari Umwami, akenyera umwenda kuko yari yambaye ubusa, yiroha mu nyanja. 
21:8 Ariko abandi bigishwa baza mu bwato, bakurura urushundura rurimo ifi kuko batari kure y'inkombe, ahubwo hari nka mikono magana abiri. 
21:9 Bomotse imusozi babona umuriro w'amakara, n'ifi zokejeho n'umutsima. 
21:10 Yesu arababwira ati “Nimuzane ku ifi mumaze gufata.”
21:11 Simoni Petero yikira mu bwato, akururira urushundura imusozi rwuzuye ifi nini ijana na mirongo itanu n'eshatu, ariko nubwo zari nyinshi zityo urushundura ntirwacitse. 
21:12 Yesu arababwira ati “Nimuze murye.” Ntihagira n'umwe wo muri abo bigishwa be utinyuka kumubaza ati “Uri nde?” Kuko bari bazi ko ari Umwami. 
21:13 Yesu araza yenda umutsima arawubaha, n'ifi na zo azigenza atyo.
21:14 Ubwo ni ubwa gatatu Yesu abonekera abigishwa be, amaze kuzuka.
21:15 Nuko bamaze kurya Yesu abaza Simoni Petero ati “Simoni mwene Yona, urusha aba kunkunda?”
21:16 Yongera kumubaza ubwa kabiri ati “Simoni mwene Yona, urankunda?”
21:17 Amubaza ubwa gatatu ati “Simoni mwene Yona, urankunda?”
21:18 Ni ukuri, ni ukuri, ndakubwira yuko ukiri umusore wikenyezaga ukajya aho ushaka hose, ariko nusaza uzarambura amaboko undi agukenyeze, akujyane aho udashaka.” 
21:19 Icyatumye avuga atyo ni ukwerekana urupfu azubahisha Imana. Amaze kuvuga atyo aramubwira ati “Nkurikira.”
21:20   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Yoh 13.25  
21:21 Petero abonye uwo abaza Yesu ati “Mwami, uyu se azamera ate?”
21:22 Yesu aramusubiza ati “Niba nshaka ko agumaho kugeza aho nzazira, upfa iki? Nkurikira.”
21:23 Ni cyo cyatumye iryo jambo ryamamara muri bene Data ngo uwo mwigishwa ntazapfa. Ariko Yesu ntiyabwiye Petero yuko uwo atazapfa, ahubwo yaramubwiye ngo “Niba nshaka ko agumaho kugeza aho nzazira, upfa iki?”
21:24 Uyu ni we wa mwigishwa uhamya ibyo, ni na we wabyanditse kandi tuzi yuko ibyo ahamya ari iby'ukuri.
21:25 Ariko hariho n'ibindi byinshi Yesu yakoze, byakwandikwa byose ngira ngo ibitabo byakwandikwa ntibyakwirwa mu isi.
